Motivation

How can we use data to improve the existing business?

How do we build the infrastructure to handle the data neccessary and provide meaning in real-time?

PERSPECTIVES

DATA SCIENCE- Most robust and inexpensive model for data

ENGINEERING - Reliable PLatform to help others innovate

BUSINESS - Deliver value from the insights provided

CHARACTERISTICS

ACCESSIBLE- Very easy to query

SCALABLE- Very easy to grow and accomodate greater volume/speeds

EFFICIENT- Low latency and low cost
